{"tid":593889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"珠三角工廠沒人應徵　老闆：80,90後年輕人嫌加班、低薪","createTime":"2018-03-15T11:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T12:00:43.000Z","uid":82845,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41d088d86dd44c97fd630db32d64e581a3e3f53f","tid":593889,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/03/15/hcRZ2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2FhcRZ2x.jpg&h=5458e0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3月份是中國廣州海珠區的城中村，一年一度的招工高潮，今年有更多的成衣工廠老闆出動，親自招兵買馬，希望能招募更多工人。但<span style=\"color: red;\">許多中國老闆感嘆，年輕人越來越不願意進工廠，「不願意加班，嫌薪水太少」</span>。老闆說以前應徵者大排長龍，現在能找到1~2個就算不錯了。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《網易》報導，到現場一看，老闆的人數比應徵者還要多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。老闆們說，<span style=\"color: red;\">以前開日薪300~400元人民幣(約新台幣1500~2000元)就招得到人，現在至少要開500~600人民幣(約新台幣2500~3000元)，才會有人願意應徵</span>。此外，老闆們也說，現在年輕人聽到要加班，都不願意做了，還有老闆形容現在找的是「打工皇帝」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，在2008年以前，算是工廠的全盛時期，以前要進工廠還可能要靠關係。但現在的年輕人，認為當工人不再是高尚職業，根本看不起工廠，寧可到大城市當業務員、房仲等，或者是當個體戶經營媒體。<span style=\"color: red;\">現在工廠的主力，大多是中年男女</span>，但近年來「換血率」極低，再過幾年，中國工廠恐怕就會邁入「高齡化」。<br />\n<br />\n報導也說，現在年輕人進廠打工主要是找對象談戀愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，順便長點見識，對於學習專業、鑽研技術，根本不感興趣，更大罵「<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">這批人已經毫無機會，失去理想，帶有絕望，未富先廢</span></strong>」。報導更稱，年輕人寧可自營自營媒體、送貨跑運輸，就是沒人要進工廠，直言未來中國的中小製造業看不到未來。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180313/1313531/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180313%2F1313531%2F&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOeu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=aaa87068\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180313%2F1313531%2F&h=2e2e9826\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180313/1313531/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同D廢老屌9後生仔心態一樣 未富先廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc79ec64ff3b5680518cba44ab5d69a59ffa087","tid":593889,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"廢到禁上下發現無錢無收入真係唔掂，就會面對現實，不過時間過去左就唔等人"},{"pid":"4f6b64939a53dd6e35675271d9735f7db44088c4","tid":593889,"uid":12628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"中共人口紅利食到完了，睇下呢班一孩政策下成長嘅公子小姐點撐起你個低端制做業賺外匯"},{"pid":"52f6fd7820b217b69cf642a749e51ade7840ccbf","tid":593889,"uid":128235,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"人當然會尋求舒適既生活，你俾既人工唔值得人地去做咪出多d，人工高你睇下有無人做？"},{"pid":"9732610f259a2ac61d2e4370f027af0974d50ccc","tid":593889,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"仲要打壓黃色產業，點得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554fbea4a70a083b9b99813bcd9622d9e4a5cc38","tid":593889,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e0aad2c08ec1cdd6ef47b327103cd1a6087ec9","tid":593889,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"所以係咁叫人生二胎<br />\n就快唔夠生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ca1ef4520aa9d7231e295923a3ec8fed2a4b45","tid":593889,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"市場終於教訓呢班賤種老細"},{"pid":"4abf21b337872a3ac039b062785d863a9d116a02","tid":593889,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e0aad2c08ec1cdd6ef47b327103cd1a6087ec9","tid":593889,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1